link: Vaclav Kotesovec, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..5000 (terms 0..1000 from Seiichi Manyama)
formula: a(n) ~ exp(4*Pi*sqrt(n)) * n^(21/4) / sqrt(2). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Jul 09 2017
